# Env-file consumed by `op run --env-file=...` for the Perplexity MCP
# server (Claude Code, ~/.claude.json mcpServers.perplexity).
#
# Only `op://<vault>/<item>/<field>` URIs are written here; op resolves
# them at exec-time so the actual API key never sits on disk in this
# repo. If a raw secret appears here it MUST be rotated immediately.
#
# Per-machine tweak: change the URI right-hand side if you store the
# key under a different vault/item/field on a given Mac (e.g. work
# 1Password account).
PERPLEXITY_API_KEY=op://Private/Perplexity API/credential
